data.description: HUGE new backyard shop! (w/plans and permits) LOVELY new backyard garden shed w/concrete patio! TONS of RV PARKING. Bring ALL your toys! Grand wooded park-like backyard perfect for BBQ's, entertaining and relaxing. Light, bright open kitchen upgraded with quartz counter tops. Dining area is positioned perfectly to behold the green, shady tranquility of the spacious backyard. The large shop has 110V and 220V electrical service, 30 Amp outlet, is insulated, has a HEATER, skylights and includes all cabinetry and workbenches! The main garage attached to the house also has 30 Amp outlet and 220V electrical service.
